fields.name: AllowedHeaders
fields.description: Required if CorsRule element is present. A list of headers allowed to be part of the cross-origin request.

fields.name: AllowedMethods
fields.description: Required if CorsRule element is present. A list of HTTP methods that are allowed to be executed by the origin.

fields.name: AllowedOrigins
fields.description: Required if CorsRule element is present. A list of origin domains that will be allowed via CORS, or "*" to allow all domains

fields.name: ExposedHeaders
fields.description: Required if CorsRule element is present. A list of response headers to expose to CORS clients.

fields.name: MaxAgeInSeconds
fields.description: Required if CorsRule element is present. The number of seconds that the client/browser should cache a preflight response.
